title: Eviction Moratorium: A Perfect Storm of Conservative Bullshit [TEASER]
itunes:title: Eviction Moratorium: A Perfect Storm of Conservative Bullshit [TEASER]
description:
Liberty and the pursuit of justice for landlords and landlords only. In this episode, the hosts talk about how the Supreme Court contorted its reading of the law to deny the Centers for Disease Control the ability to ban eviction during the pandemic.

The full version of this premium episode is available exclusively to our Patreon supporters. To join, visit www.patreon.com/fivefourpod. 


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
